{"tid":2179652,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公司同事工作時間拍YouTube片比老細鬧","createTime":"2020-08-29T09:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T09:57:28.000Z","uid":158145,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf83491cb2c24eef2d32ed20ba1bbca6d8f070f","tid":2179652,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"首先佢係個曼聯球迷<br />\n佢個channel 都係講下曼聯既新聞/消息<br />\n個channel 都有6000幾個訂閱<br />\n<br />\n我老細都係曼聯fans<br />\n同時老細都有睇佢channel<br />\n所以佢都隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n<br />\n但係前兩日佢有條片<br />\n放咗唔少廣告<br />\n老細睇幾分鐘就彈一次廣告（老細聲稱）<br />\n<br />\n老細嬲起上黎走出房鬧佢<br />\n話佢平時已經用工作時間拍片<br />\n仲要插廣告賺錢<br />\n<br />\n佢同老細講廣告係YouTube方面決定<br />\nYouTuber係控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老細死死地氣走返入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6a908fc9c1f531076a1a8e4386b6d211f80c0d","tid":2179652,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"冇人理？"},{"pid":"b581e4138e49d568fe66be4ed24696b08b5edae3","tid":2179652,"uid":164167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"廣告同12碼一樣多"},{"pid":"1071c555a6260c1455a913facd388af918aa892d","tid":2179652,"uid":215794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"同老細講：<br />\nQuit Youtube囉"},{"pid":"fbf641bbe5754bae247aabbdd3602fc7802dc386","tid":2179652,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"你個同事係大爸？"},{"pid":"1b58ff7d7785ac0ec994fa36540aef5ee39a4a83","tid":2179652,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf641bbe5754bae247aabbdd3602fc7802dc386","tid":2179652,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"你個同事係大爸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"唔係佢<img src=\"/